# SourceA public copy language law (LOCKED)

Founder explanations, architecture notes, strategy, repo terminology, governance jargon, and agent instructions are **INTERNAL by default**.

## Classify every source statement before editing public HTML

| Class | Where it may appear |
|-------|---------------------|
| **INTERNAL** | `docs/`, `brain-os/`, `archive/`, `.cursor/`, `investor/` (private deck), comments, receipts |
| **CUSTOMER-FACING** | Product + sales pages: `/`, `/sourcea/offer`, `/sourcea/pricing`, `/sourcea/platform`, `/sourcea/growth`, `/sourcea/team`, `/sourcea/proof`, `/start`, case studies |
| **INVESTOR-FACING** | `/sourcea/investors` only — no UI clones, no fake traction; still avoid raw founder jargon |

**Only CUSTOMER-FACING content on product and sales pages.**

## Customer-facing writing rules

- Buyer POV: problem → outcome → how it works → trust → cost → next step
- Plain language; no assumption the reader knows Noetfield internals
- Do **not** use on customer pages unless the page is explicitly for technical buyers **and** the term is necessary: motor, receipt (as jargon), promotion, control plane, proof chain, orchestration, governance layer, architecture, pipeline, agent lane, runtime state, Factory/Runtime/Proof stack names, PASS/BLOCK as product vocabulary, DFY, governed, orchestrate, dispatch, on disk
- Do not paste research notes, internal comparisons, roadmap debates, or agent instructions into copy
- If a section answers none of: (1) problem (2) result (3) how (4) trust (5) cost (6) next step — **remove it**

## Technical-buyer exception

`/sourcea/platform`, `/eval`, `/sourcea/kernel/`, API code samples: minimal necessary engineering terms only. Prefer buyer outcomes in headings; put API field names in `<code>` samples only.

## Final law

> Internal truth informs the page. Internal language must not appear on the page.

Before ship: `bash scripts/verify-static-www.sh` when touching www; spot-check edited HTML for banned terms with `rg -i 'proof chain|governance receipt|orchestrat|control plane|agent lane|on disk|PASS/BLOCK' sites/SourceA-landing/green-unified/*.html`
